    "• We selected the molecular type as 'TF' and chose the 'Periph-eral_blood' tissue type, with 21 cases remaining.",
    "• There are 11 datasets included in the PBMCs cell type in the single-cell data.",
    "• We chose the TF expressed in single-cell data and with known motifs available, and 8 datasets remained.",
    "We download the PBMC 10K data from the 10× Genomics website (https://support.10xgenomics.com/single-cell-multiome-atac-gex/ datasets).",
    "Note that it contains 11,909 cells, and the granulocytes were removed by cell sorting of this dataset."
